0x___1 = Slave in 'INIT' state
0x___2 = Slave in 'PREOP' state
0x___3 = Slave in 'BOOT' state
0x___4 = Slave in 'SAFEOP' state
0x___8 = Slave in 'OP' state]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><BitOffs>0</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>suffix</Name><Type>EtherCATSuffix</Type><Comment><![CDATA[prefix code
0x001_ = Slave signals error
0x002_ = Invalid vendorId, productCode... read
0x004_ = Initialization error occurred
0x008_ = Slave disabled
0x010_ = Slave not present
0x020_ = Slave signals link error
0x040_ = Slave signals missing link
0x080_ = Slave signals unexpected link
0x100_ = Communication port A
0x200_ = Communication port B
0x400_ = Communication port C
0x800_ = Communication port D]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><BitOffs>16</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>isFault</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[TRUE if either state is not 8 and code exists]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>32</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>colour</Name><Type>DWORD</Type><Comment><![CDATA[colour state]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs></SubItem></DataType><DataType><Name Namespace="Tc2_EtherCAT">ST_EcCrcError</Name><BitSize>96</BitSize><SubItem><Name>portA</Name><Type>UDINT</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>0</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>portB</Name><Type>UDINT</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>32</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>portC</Name><Type>UDINT</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs></SubItem></DataType><DataType><Name>typeEtherCATIndicator</Name><BitSize>992</BitSize><SubItem><Name>currentState</Name><Type>typeEtherCATState</Type><Comment><![CDATA[inside colour]]></Comment><BitSize>96</BitSize><BitOffs>0</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>historicalState</Name><Type>typeEtherCATState</Type><Comment><![CDATA[outside colour]]></Comment><BitSize>96</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>SlaveNumber</Name><Type>UINT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[slave number 1-65535]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><BitOffs>192</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>isPresent</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[TRUE if node is present in config]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>208</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>ConfigData</Name><Type Namespace="Tc2_EtherCAT">ST_EcSlaveConfigData</Type><Comment><![CDATA[extra diagnostics]]></Comment><BitSize>640</BitSize><BitOffs>224</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>crcCount</Name><Type Namespace="Tc2_EtherCAT">ST_EcCrcError</Type><BitSize>96</BitSize><BitOffs>864</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>hmiNum</Name><Type>UINT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[PLC ordering number]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><BitOffs>960</BitOffs></SubItem></DataType><DataType><Name>typeDPSlaveIndicator</Name><BitSize>96</BitSize><SubItem><Name>currentState</Name><Type>DWORD</Type><Comment><![CDATA[inside colour]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>0</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>historicalState</Name><Type>DWORD</Type><Comment><![CDATA[outside colour]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>32</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>SlaveNumber</Name><Type>UINT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[slave number 1-127]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs></SubItem></DataType><DataType><Name>typePROFINETState</Name><BitSize>96</BitSize><SubItem><Name>state</Name><Type>PROFINETstate</Type><Comment><![CDATA[PnIoBoxState
UINT
0 = No error
1 = Profinet device state machine is in boot mode
2 = Device not found
3 = The stationname is not unique
4 = IP could not be set
5 = IP conflict
6 = DCP set was not successful
7 = Watchdog error
8 = Datahold error
9 = RTC3: Sync mode could not be initiated
10 = Profinet controller has a link error
11 = The aliasname is not unique
12 = The automatic name assignement isn't possible - wrong device type
13 = IOC-AR is established but no application ready
14 = IOC-AR is established but module difference
15 = At least one InputCR is invalid, provider in stop or problemindicator is set
16 = At least one OutputCR is invalid, provider in stop or problemindicator is set
31 = Only for EtherCAT gateways: WC-State of cyclic EtherCAT frame is 1]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><BitOffs>0</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>suffix</Name><Type>PROFINETSuffix</Type><Comment><![CDATA[PnIoBoxDiag
UINT
0x0000 = No diagnosis
0x0001 = IOC-AR is not established
0x0002 = IOC-AR is established
0x0004 = IOC-AR is established but no application ready
0x0008 = IOC-AR is established but module difference
0x0010 = At least one AlarmCR got a diagnosis alarm
0x0100 = At least one InputCR is invalid
0x0200 = At least one InputCR Provider is in stop
0x0400 = At least one InputCR Problemindicator is set
0x1000 = At least one OutputCR is invalid
0x2000 = At least one OutputCR Provider is in stop
0x4000 = At least one OutputCR Problemindicator is set]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><BitOffs>16</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>isFault</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[TRUE if either state is not 8 and code exists]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>32</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>colour</Name><Type>DWORD</Type><Comment><![CDATA[colour state]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs></SubItem></DataType><DataType><Name>typePROFINETIndicator</Name><BitSize>224</BitSize><SubItem><Name>currentState</Name><Type>typePROFINETState</Type><Comment><![CDATA[inside colour]]></Comment><BitSize>96</BitSize><BitOffs>0</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>historicalState</Name><Type>typePROFINETState</Type><Comment><![CDATA[outside colour]]></Comment><BitSize>96</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>SlaveNumber</Name><Type>UINT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[slave number 1-65535]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><BitOffs>192</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>isPresent</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[TRUE if node is present in config]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>208</BitOffs></SubItem></DataType><DataType><Name>typeProfiNetMaster</Name><BitSize>48</BitSize><SubItem><Name>DevState</Name><Type>UINT</Type><BitSize>16</BitSize><BitOffs>0</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>PnIoError</Name><Type>UINT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[0x0001 = No link AT port 1
0x0002 = No link at port 2
